<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>عنْ جابِرِ بنِ عَبدِ اللَّهِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>قالَه خالِدُ بنُ يَزيدَ، عَنْ سَعيدِ بنِ أَبي هِلالٍ، عَنْ رَجُلٍ <span class="c2">(١)</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[٨٤٣٩]</span> عَليٌّ <span class="c2">(٣)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>سَمِعَ أَبا ذر <span class="c2">(٤)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>رَوى عَنهُ ابنُهُ الضَّحّاكُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>* * *<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
